TAXONOMY: The whiteÂ­eared Neotropical 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Linnaeus" authorityYear="1758" box="[123,236,1029,1052]" class="Mammalia" family="Didelphidae" genus="Didelphis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Didelphimorphia" pageId="17" pageNumber="18" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">
